     Subkey fingerprint: 62C9 E5F4 DA30 0D94 AC36  166B E206 C29F BF04 FF17
GPG verified '/home/marcilr/.rvm/archives/rvm-1.29.3.tgz'

Installing RVM to /home/marcilr/.rvm/
    Adding rvm PATH line to /home/marcilr/.profile /home/marcilr/.mkshrc \
/home/marcilr/.bashrc /home/marcilr/.zshrc.
