/home/marcilr/.bash_profile /home/marcilr/.zlogin.
Installation of RVM in /home/marcilr/.rvm/ is almost complete:

  * To start using RVM you need to run `source \
/home/marcilr/.rvm/scripts/rvm`
    in all your open shell windows, in rare cases you need to \
reopen all shell windows.
$ 

$ type rvm
rvm is /home/marcilr/.rvm/bin/rvm
$ 

Looks good!
